   <talk_paragraph index="n040_king_casius-1-a" image="QN_Npc_Bishop.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n040_king_casius-1-b" mid="146"><![CDATA[<html>What is he doing now?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="145"><![CDATA[<html>$King Cassius$<BR>The adventurers who came with you are still working hard under <FONT color=#a82424>Ignacio</FONT>. He's been great. Since my uncle and the General are all busy cleaning up after the battle, he volunteered to cleanse the Black Dragon's evil power and conduct a <FONT color=#a82424>ritual for the kingdom</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n040_king_casius-1-b" image="QW_46.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n040_king_casius-2" mid="148"><![CDATA[<html>Sunken Cargo Vessel?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="147"><![CDATA[<html>$King Cassius$<BR>Oh... not too long ago, someone went to the <FONT color=#a82424>Sunken Cargo Vessel</FONT> with a Crystal Calabash.<BR>He said he was going to pour something into it.... But, I'm not sure.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n040_king_casius-2" image="QW_46.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="149"><![CDATA[<html>$King Cassius$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, are you also going to the <FONT color=#a82424>Sunken Cargo Vessel</FONT>?<BR>You're worried about the colleague who went ahead, aren't you?<BR>You're such a kind girl....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n525_edan-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n525_edan-2-a" mid="153"><![CDATA[<html>What are you doing?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="151"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan${action:Talk}<BR>Oh, it's <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.<BR>What are you doing here?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n525_edan-2-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n525_edan-2-b" mid="155"><![CDATA[<html>You shouldn't help the Bishop.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="154"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan$<BR>I was collecting the <FONT color=#a82424>Sea Beasts' Soul</FONT> into this Crystal Calabash.<BR>I think I've collected enough, so I was going to go back and report.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n525_edan-2-b" image="QN_Npc_Bishop.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n525_edan-2-c" mid="157"><![CDATA[<html>I'm from the future. So... I know.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="156"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan$<BR>...Why are you saying that suddenly?<BR>Do you have a specific reason to suspect the Bishop?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n525_edan-2-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n525_edan-2-d" mid="159"><![CDATA[<html>That's... (I can't say that right now)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="158"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan$<BR>Your future...? <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, it's not that I don't trust you.<BR>
But, if that future was a fixed, definite future, why are you here? Also, why did you follow me without deciding on what to do next?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n525_edan-2-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="160"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan$<BR>As you, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT> have something to do, it's the same for me, too.<BR>I'm not happy with you stirring an internal turmoil with uncertain information. Goodbye.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n525_edan-3" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="161"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan$<BR>I respect <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>'s courage and skill.<BR>I hope we could have a chance to work with each other some other day. Now, goodbye.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n040_king_casius-3" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="162"><![CDATA[<html>$King Cassius$<BR>Had a safe trip to Sunken Cargo Vessel?<BR>You're face is so grim.... You're making me sad....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-3" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-3-a" mid="164"><![CDATA[<html>What should I do?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="163"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine${sound:npc_MR_Jasmin_sp_01.ogg}<BR>So, <FONT color=#a82424>Cleric Edan</FONT> didn't believe your story?<BR>...Even if he does, it'll be hard to get suspicious at the <FONT color=#a82424>Bishop</FONT>.<BR>Afterall, He is a Cleric and the Bishop was his Boss.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-3-a" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="165"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine$<BR>What does Velskud say?<BR>Ask him for advice at the <FONT color=#a82424>Foothills of Black Mountain</FONT>. It troubles me since it's a Sea Beast.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n523_velskud-3" image="QM_Sea_Drake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n523_velskud-3-a" mid="167"><![CDATA[<html>Serpent?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="166"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>Sea beast...?<BR>Are you talking about the <FONT color=#a82424>Serpentra</FONT> which we've killed 50 years ago?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n523_velskud-3-a" image="QM_Sea_Drake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n523_velskud-3-b" mid="169"><![CDATA[<html>It may resurrect.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="168"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>Yes. <FONT color=#a82424>Serpentra</FONT>. It caused much violence at Lorreline River near Saint Haven; therefore, we eliminated it 50 years ago. It was impossible to completely annihilate it, so it was separated into many pieces and <FONT color=#a82424>sealed</FONT>. There is no chance of it reviving.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n523_velskud-3-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n523_velskud-3-c" mid="171"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="170"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>Is that how it's recorded in your future?<BR>.... Then the reason why he tampered with my core was to get the energy to revive the Serpentra.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n523_velskud-3-c" image="QN_Npc_Bishop.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n523_velskud-3-d" mid="173"><![CDATA[<html>What should I do?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="172"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>He is a member of a group called the <FONT color=#a82424>Apostle</FONT>.<BR>His purpose must have been to penetrate Saint Haven from the inside and disturb the church.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n523_velskud-3-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n523_velskud-4" mid="175"><![CDATA[<html>But...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="174"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>Didn't I tell you? It's their responsibility when fools cause regrettable results.<BR>Just leave the fools alone.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n523_velskud-4" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="176"><![CDATA[<html>$Velskud$<BR>Even if you work for others, if they don't understand you, your attempt goes in vain.<BR>I've seen one like you, but to me, it's only a futile attempt.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-4" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-4-a" mid="178"><![CDATA[<html>We have to stop it!!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="177"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine${sound:npc_MR_Jasmin_sp_01.ogg}<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Serpentra</FONT>? Of course... Our records weren't wrong.<BR>I'm so worried. If we leave it like this, Saint Haven will be attacked again by the Serpentra.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-4-a" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-4-b" mid="180"><![CDATA[<html>What? What did you say?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="179"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine$<BR>......Is it a right thing to stop this....<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jasmine mumbles without confidence.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-4-b" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-4-c" mid="182"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="181"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine$<BR>If every event doesn't flow according to the set future, there may be more problems that what we anticipated.<BR>
We ran into a reality where we can't do anything about it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-4-c" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-4-d" mid="184"><![CDATA[<html>We may be able to save this place!!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="183"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine$<BR>If you try something and change the history, the end may come earlier.<BR>
It will be a shame if the end comes in at <FONT color=#a82424>that time</FONT> before we even finish saving the world here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-4-d" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-4-e" mid="186"><![CDATA[<html>I didn't fOgret.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="185"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine${sound:npc_SH_Jasmin_sp_06.ogg}<BR>Save that place? <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jasmine laughs at your reasoning.)<BR></FONT>What you need to save is our time, not there.<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, did you fOgret about your mission?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n393_academic_station-4-e" image="QN_Npc_Academic_jasmine.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n393_academic_station-4-f" mid="188"><![CDATA[<html>...That's my destiny.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="187"><![CDATA[<html>$Academic Jasmine$<BR>
Then, leave the Serpentra alone. It's bound to revive.<BR>Anyway, you must watch carefully and when the Nest is lifted, take the <FONT color=#a82424>Prophet</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
